description: Nicole Kidman stars in a juicy, nifty little end-of-summer mystery on Netflix — where the people are beautiful, the arguments are public and sloppy, the house is gorgeous and the drinks are bottomless.
title: 'The Perfect Couple' is 6 episodes of simple, soapy fun

description: The magnetic bond between Gillian Welch and David Rawlings, partners in life and in music, has always been central to their songs. On their latest album, the "we" becomes existential.
title: 'Woodland' is the sound of Gillian Welch and David Rawlings rebuilding together following disaster

description: Taylor Fritz surged with a six-game run against a fading Frances Tiafoe, also of the U.S., to come out on top 4-6, 7-5, 4-6, 6-4, 6-1 and reach his first Grand Slam final.
title: Taylor Fritz wins match to become first American man in a U.S. Open final since 2006

description: The spacecraft landed in New Mexico early Saturday morning leaving two astronauts behind on the International Space Station. The crew members will return to earth in February aboard a SpaceX craft.
title: With no crew aboard, spacecraft Starliner lands without a hitch
